	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would like to know what is the best web site for Magician (info, strategies, quest).  I would like to get more info before starting a Dark Elf Mage<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
